  <h3>About this game</h3>

  <p>Discover the mysterious world of <strong>The Mistbrewer</strong>, a distinctive <strong>Match-3 style puzzle game</strong>, designed to be instantly accessible while providing a depth of strategy for those looking to delve further.</p>

  <div class="screenshot">
    <%= image_tag "mistbrewer_screenshot.jpg", alt: "The Mistbrewer", title: "The Mistbrewer" %>
  </div>

  <p>Enjoy the relaxing visual design and soothing piano melodies as you navigate your way through the game.<p>


  <h3>Features</h3>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Accessibility and Depth:</strong> Add reagents to your brew and combine them in groups of three to evolve them and discover new reagents. The game's intuitive approach conceals a strategic depth that unveils itself with the addition of new ingredients.</li>

    <li><strong>Unique Active Skills:</strong> Use three unique active skills to devise strategies and unlock challenging situations.</li>

    <li><strong>Passive Talents:</strong> Explore dozens of passive talents that will fundamentally change your gameplay style, leading to an even more varied experience.</li>

    <li><strong>Story Mode:</strong> Progress at your own pace through 10 captivating chapters. Each chapter offers an opportunity to hone your skills and understand the game mechanics better.</li>

    <li><strong>Adventure+:</strong> After completing the story mode, accept a new challenge. This harder reprise of the story offers an increasing challenge with each new playthrough. Every victory unlocks a higher difficulty level, ensuring limitless replayability.</li>

    <li><strong>Endless Mode:</strong> Play as long as you like with the Endless mode, where your endurance is your only limit. Keep track of your progress with persistent scores.</li>

    <li><strong>A Relaxing Universe:</strong> Lose yourself in the world of The Mistbrewer, characterized by soothing graphics and gentle piano melodies. Ambient animations further enrich this calm and enveloping universe.</li>

    <li><strong>Replayability:</strong> Between the Story mode, Adventure +, and Endless, The Mistbrewer offers hours of thoughtful and relaxing entertainment. Each game mode provides a new way to stimulate your strategic mind.</li>

  </ul>


  <p>Immerse yourself in the nebulous and tranquil world of The Mistbrewer.</p>


